    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Buildings or groups of buildings containing auditoriums, multipurpose spaces, and auxiliary facilities suitable for the presentation of various performing arts, such as concerts, operas, and plays.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Edificio o grupo de edificios que contiene auditorios, espacios multiuosos, e instalaciones auxiliares adecuadas para la presentación de varias artes representativas, tales como conciertos, óperas y obras de teatro.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Gebruikt voor gebouwen of groepen gebouwen die auditoria, multifunctionele ruimten en aanvullende voorzieningen bevatten die geschikt zijn voor de opvoering van verschillende uitvoerende kunsten, zoals concerten, opera's, balletuitvoeringen en toneelstukken.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>建築物或建築物群，內部包含觀眾席、多用途空間、和輔助設施，適合用來呈現各類型的表演藝術，像是演奏會、歌劇和戲劇。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
